   "viva": "'Suspected malignant cord compression — I would give dexamethasone 16 mg now, arrange an urgent MRI of the whole spine within 24 hours, refer to radiation oncology and neurosurgery, and document neurology and ambulatory status as my baseline.' Mention consent considerations for surgery vs radiotherapy and the prognostic value of pre-treatment mobility.",
   "mnemonic": "'Steroids Move Radiotherapy' = Steroids -> MRI whole spine -> Radiotherapy/surgery, in that order.",
