   "viva": "'Symptomatic brain metastases with raised ICP — I would give dexamethasone for the vasogenic oedema, image with contrast MRI, refer to radiation oncology/neurosurgery, and importantly I would NOT start prophylactic anticonvulsants unless the patient has had a seizure.'",
