   "viva": "Out loud: 'Screening is only for asymptomatic people. This patient has a red flag - painless visible haematuria / postmenopausal bleeding / iron-deficiency anaemia - so I'd refer for diagnostic work-up urgently and not rely on the recent normal screening result.'",
