   "viva": "Out loud: 'Onset of irAEs is variable - skin first, then colitis and hepatitis, then endocrine effects, and they can be delayed even after the drug is ceased, so I always ask about recent or recently-ceased immunotherapy in anyone with new organ inflammation.'",
