   "viva": "Examiner: 'On high-dose morphine, now jerking and more pain — what's happening and what do you do?' Answer: opioid neurotoxicity → reduce/rotate to different opioid at lower dose + hydrate + treat reversibles; pick fentanyl in renal failure. Discriminator: hyperalgesia vs under-treatment.",
