   "mcqTrap": "'Prescribe docusate' or 'add psyllium/fibre supplement' for a patient starting morphine — tempting because they sound gentle, but docusate alone is ineffective and bulk-forming laxatives are unsafe in this group. Correct = regular senna ± macrogol started with the opioid.",
